quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,141,No kugira ngo Allah agaragaze abemera ndetse anoreke abahakanyi
  3,142,Cyangwa mwibwira ko muzinjira mu ijuru Allah atari yabagerageza ngo yerekane abaharaniye inzira ye n’abihangana muri mwe
  3,143,Nyamara mwajyaga mwifuza urupfu (kugwa ku rugamba rutagatifu) mbere y’uko muhura na rwo. Ngaho murarubonye n’amaso yanyu
  3,144,Kandi Muhamadi nta kindi ari cyo uretse kuba intumwa yanabanjirijwe n’izindi ntumwa. Ese aramutse apfuye cyangwa akicwa mwahita muhindukira (mugasubira mu buhakanyi)? N’uzahindukira nta cyo bizatwara Allah;kandi Allah azagororera abashimira
  3,145,"Kandi nta muntu wapfa bitari ku bushake bwa Allah no ku gihe cyagenwe. N’uzashaka ingororano zo ku isi tuzazimuha, ndetse n’uzashaka ingororano zo ku munsi w’imperuka tuzazimuha. Kandi ni ukuri tuzagororera abashimira"
  3,146,"Ni bangahe mu bahanuzi barwanye bari kumwe n’abayoboke babo benshi, ariko ntibatezuka kubera ibyababayeho mu nzira ya Allah, ntibanacika intege ndetse ntibanaba ingaruzwamuheto. Kandi Allah akunda abihangana"
  3,147,"Nta rindi jambo ryabarangaga uretse kuvuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Tubabarire ibyaha byacu no kurengera kwacu mu byo dukora; uhe ibirenge byacu gushikama, udutabare, kandi uduhe gutsinda abahakanyi"
  3,148,Nuko Allah abaha ingororano zo ku isi n’ingororano zihebuje zo ku munsi w’imperuka. Kandi Allah akunda abakora ibyiza